## 4. Test Environment

### 4.1 Environment Requirements

|  |  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Environment | URL | Database | Purpose |
| Local Dev | http://localhost:3000 | SQLite (local) | Development testing |
| SIT | http://localhost:3000 | SQLite with seeded data | Integration testing |

### 4.2 Browser Requirements

|  |  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Browser | Version | OS | Required |
| Chrome | 90+ | Windows/Mac | Yes |
| Firefox | 90+ | Windows/Mac | Yes |
| Edge | 90+ | Windows | Yes |

### 4.3 Test Data Requirements

|  |  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Data Type | Description | Source | Preparation |
| Stale KB entries | Entries with staleness\_score > 0.8, last\_reviewed\_at > 90 days ago | SQLite seed | Insert via SQL |
| Fresh KB entries | Entries with staleness\_score = 0 | SQLite seed | Insert via SQL |
| Empty state | No stale entries | SQLite | Delete all stale entries |

### 4.4 External Dependencies

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| System | Dependency | Mock/Stub Available |
| MCP Server | Running with /api/kb/\* endpoints | No — use real server |

