## 7. Risk & Mitigation

|  |  |  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| # | Risk | Impact | Likelihood | Mitigation |
| 1 | API endpoint not returning expected format | High | Low | Verify API response format before UI testing |
| 2 | basePath not set in test environment | Medium | Medium | Ensure nav-bar.js is loaded before dashboard.js |
| 3 | Animation timing varies across browsers | Low | Medium | Accept ±50ms variance |

## 8. Defect Management

### 8.1 Severity Levels

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Severity | Definition | Example |
| Critical | Feature completely broken | Mark Reviewed button doesn’t call API |
| Major | Feature partially broken, workaround exists | Toast doesn’t show but row is removed |
| Minor | UI issue, cosmetic | Animation slightly jerky |
| Trivial | Typo, minor alignment | Button padding off by 1px |

### 8.2 Priority Levels

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Priority | Definition | SLA |
| P1 | Must fix immediately | 4 hours |
| P2 | Must fix before release | 1 business day |
| P3 | Should fix if time permits | 3 business days |
| P4 | Nice to fix, can defer | Next release |

## 9. Test Metrics & Reporting

### 9.1 Metrics

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Metric | Formula | Target |
| Test Execution Rate | Executed / Total × 100% | 100% |
| Pass Rate | Passed / Executed × 100% | ≥ 95% |
| Critical Defect Count | Count of Critical severity | 0 |

